projects.name: Bone Fracture Detection
projects.description: Developed a deep learning-based system for automated bone fracture detection leveraging CNNs and the MURA dataset. Implemented a two-stage process involving initial classification with ResNet50 and subsequent fracture detection using tailored CNN models for each bone type. Achieved high accuracy rates in both bone part classification and fracture detection, demonstrating the potential for enhancing diagnostic workflows.
